{"tid":1521002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新指揮官：勿叫「曱甴」免惹麻煩","createTime":"2019-08-31T04:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T04:48:49.000Z","uid":279819,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7789352f948e0daa9bc97c24d459a60e42113b63","tid":1521002,"uid":279819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:29:01.000Z","msg":"蘋果<br />\n【本報訊】香港警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉過去曾於公開信以「曱甴」侮辱示威市民，甚至有警員多次被拍到在衝突場合以「曱甴」形容示威者。本地英文網媒HKFP報道，剛調派到荃灣警區的新任助理指揮官邵豐祺（Simon Southgate ，圓圖），周二曾向其所屬警區警員發電郵，提醒警員要嚴守紀律及操守，不要讓公眾有任何機會投訴警隊。<br />\n<br />\nHKFP報道，邵豐祺在電郵中指出，社會上有部份人士現時對警隊非常不滿，對方會用盡每一個機會，去投訴警員及踩低警隊。邵豐祺在電郵中列舉3項須糾正的警員行為，第一項就提醒警員切勿以「曱甴」形容示威者。他指，即使示威者作出任何程度暴力及違法行為，警員都不值得因「曱甴」論為自己帶來麻煩。<br />\n相關新聞：遊行被禁 今日自由行<br />\n<br />\nEQ低屢引發警民罵戰<br />\n邵豐祺又叮囑同袍要保持鎮定及保持高EQ，無論對方如何無禮，警員都應避免用粗口及粗魯行徑回應。他又指，早前收到一宗投訴，有警員被拍攝到當值時未有佩戴警帽，要求注意制服配置。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，邵豐祺調任荃灣區助理指揮官（行政）前，曾出任警隊服務質素監察部警司，主管警隊服務標準。警方在處理反送中示威期間的情商表現屢被詬病，在昨日凌晨的深水埗大拘捕行動結束後，一名警務人員被拍攝到大叫：「又拉到人真開心，垃圾！」片段由恒生大學學生會編委會所拍，報道並指警員在收隊前與街上民眾對罵。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭啟源"},{"pid":"7cd9582141a1b5eae45e12ce5b937e6729ee1c1d","tid":1521002,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:30:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">830 大濫捕 黑警被斬 完全將焦點轉移<br />\n<br />\n請記住 今日出黎目的係<br />\n<br />\n因為5年前831中共就普選設下「提名委員會」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我要真普選！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今日港島見！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"54afbb211758419b268acb57ff532488b51783ef","tid":1521002,"uid":139173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUpTHxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUpTHxB.jpg&h=6bd49a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n政府急住要喺831決戰<br />\n因為驚九月機場同三罷<br />\n不受傷不被捕<br />\n九月份繼續齊上齊落<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n員佐級協會不接受個別指揮官個人意見"},{"pid":"ccee085b42007ee4465a67cf1d2d645e0e1624a4","tid":1521002,"uid":287387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:32:09.000Z","msg":"亡羊補牢"},{"pid":"8b4e688e6578659d0ca8cf9c6b6972fdc1a9a42b","tid":1521002,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da5056a89e8621d11b56483de3da3629f06bb0f","tid":1521002,"uid":95221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:42:01.000Z","msg":"警隊服務質素監察部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係識監察"},{"pid":"7444d50e380540e4826f5ae4956096ad4e125799","tid":1521002,"uid":164374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:42:07.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，呢 d 碎料無人 care, 叫班狗唔好私行酷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a83f670062ff3b7b3c146130d631a5990341071","tid":1521002,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:42:47.000Z","msg":"繼續叫啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s